V0.11 Qwen30b OK w/ CUDA graphs, etc.: 80tk/s single request, 2300tk/s 256 requests, less than 2 minutes to ingest 256 requests: https://gist.github.com/Zidrewndacht/cfbd17b3dcf9636f49c70350d283d699 

V0.16 Qwen30b w/ CUDA graphs, etc.: 130tk/s single request (good!) but 0tk/s mixed prefill-decode, can't even ingest ~30 requests after ~5 minutes: https://gist.github.com/Zidrewndacht/299149862ba0ff4533fb17d0f5d49e0a

